data.description:
Looking for great value in today's market? Put this solidly built home on your list! This home features an eat in kitchen open to the living
room. The upper level has a walk out deck with great view over the private backyard. The lower level has a large bedroom and 1/2 BA. You
will find plenty of storage in a bonus room plus oversized garage. Book your showing today.
